{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_01","textHome":"我家的中华料理店，从父辈开始就快倒了……@可母亲和奶奶依旧每日挥霍无度……@但是，面对这样一家子总要有人能担起责任！@那么，我，由比鹤乃！@总有一天会成为成大事立大业的人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_18","textHome":"好，完成了！右腿单立保持了24小时！@好漫长啊……说来，这个训练比起消耗体力，@更像是在与无聊做斗争啊。@不过，左腿也来练一下吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_19","textHome":"还不够还不够还不够！……我还要变的更强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_20","textHome":"嗯嗯，这样确实上了一个台阶！肯定没错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_21","textHome":"听我说呀！我就稍微练了练拳脚，@旁边的野猫就摔得四脚朝天了！@没错……肯定是我变强了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_22","textHome":"我做到啦！前阵子去动物园的时候，@我让狮子坐下了哟！就站在笼子前，@心里想着「坐下！」而已~！@我好像达到这种境界了呢"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_23","textHome":"嗯？新闻？「海豚秀上海豚发飙了」？@啊，确实是我！我在观众席上想着@「要是跳得再卖力点不是很帅吗？」，@它们就感觉到了！虽然我也不懂是什么原理！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_24","textHome":"哦！久等啦！好，那我开始！@一、二！「称霸夏天也能称之为最强！」@喂，一起喊嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_25","textHome":"早上吼！@清早就游过了一公里，现在状态极佳！@今天我也是最强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_26","textHome":"在海之家吃到的炒面真是棒极了。@那么！就用那里的面，@加上佐料做成中式炒面怎么样！@是个挣钱的机会嘞！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_27","textHome":"傍晚时西沉的夏阳，仿佛燃烧一样耀眼……嗯……突然想出去跑跑……我去去就回！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_03","textHome":"竟然是要和我谈心吗……没事没事！@我应该尝试各种事情！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_28","textHome":"装点夜空的美丽烟花……@突然很想试试点火发射！@由我来抱着烟花筒，把超大的球形烟花给……@诶，不行吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_29","textHome":"要对抗夏日的暑气……那就让自己也变热！@只要点燃内心，就不需要空调！@以前的我这样说着，然后中暑倒下了……@不要太勉强哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":201}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_30","textHome":"虽然有突发事件让人挺难办的，@但真遇到了的话，也能留下不错的回忆。@就是……「什么都行，放马过来！」的意思。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_31","textHome":"嗯……这样啊……@说到这个……就是像鬼屋一样的东西！@所以，接下来就是试胆大会！@不是吗……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_32","textHome":"哦，大家要一起玩吗？@嗯？不是吗？啊，知道了知道了！@是要噼里啪啦地打起来了吧！带我一个！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_33","textHome":"游泳前的准备运动是鹤乃体操！@而且是第二部！开始！@手指竖起来，两手前推……@然后抓！再抓！抓一百下！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_34","textHome":"嘿！来冲浪吧！用这个！@对，是中华锅！没问题没问题！@应该能用！虽然没试过！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_35","textHome":"怎、怎么会……不是吧？@快告诉我不是真的！@我……我无法接受！@刨冰的糖浆原来都是一个味道吗！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":300,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_36","textHome":"虽然海上的战斗也说得通，@但是要想象一下才行。@海的话……在船上……随着海浪摇晃……@钓着鱼……很开心！啊，搞错了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_51_37","textHome":"代表夏天的花，当然是向日葵了！@我也很喜欢！因为……葵花子很好吃嘛！@推荐用一点盐炒熟吃哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_04",